    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out. I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream! If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
