    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system for a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with the factory variable M-differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed with surgical precision: the VANOS unit has been overhauled with Beisan components, rod bearings replaced with ACL race bearings, and the rear subframe reinforced with structural plates to ensure chassis longevity. The suspension geometry remains true, benefitting from refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers. With original paint depth consistent across all panels and an interior devoid of bolster wear or plastic degradation, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
